@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
title Structure of the CIP repository

folder "cardano-foundation/CIPs" {
  [README.md\nmaster index] as IDX
  folder "CIP-XXXX/" {
    [README.md\nproposal text] as CIPR
    [supporting assets] as ASSET
  }
  folder "CPS-XXXX/" {
    [README.md\nproblem statement] as CPSR
  }
  [CIP-0001\nCIP process] as C1
  [CIP-9999\nCPS process] as C9999
  [.github/CIP-TEMPLATE.md\nCPS-TEMPLATE.md] as TMPL
}

IDX --> CIPR : lists number,\ntitle, status
IDX --> CPSR : lists CPSs
C1 ..> CIPR : governs
C9999 ..> CPSR : governs
TMPL ..> CIPR : scaffolds
CPSR --> CIPR : "Proposed Solutions" /\n"Solution To" links

note bottom of CIPR
  Header carries the
  Category field: one of
  Meta, Ledger, Consensus,
  Network, Wallets, Tokens,
  Metadata, Plutus, Tools
end note
@enduml
